o) ipc.h
   Defines various common data-types used between userland and kernel.
o) system.h / ipc_system.c
   Handles IPC initialization and system call.
o) mailbox.h / ipc_mailbox.c
   Header defines common mailbox structure and lays out (in text) the mailbox
   layout.  Source has mailbox processing code  as called as system call.
o) port.h / ipc_port.c
   Defines port data types and API.
o) msg.h / ipc_msg.c
   Message processing and delivery.
o) right.h / ipc_right.c
   Port rights system.
o) service.h / ipc_service.c
   Services infrastructure.
o) data.h / ipc_data.c
   Data descriptor processing.
